text:
The bustling Wood Ward of [[Fairhaven]] is the home of the famous [[Distant Exchange]], a vibrant and exotic marketplace. It is also home to a [[Jorasco]] [[enclave]].

!! Noteworthy Locations

* the [[Distant Exchange]]
* [[Jorasco Enclave (Fairhaven)]]
* ''Red Maple'' (inn)
* ''Row's End Tavern''
title: Wood Ward
